text.textblock: Establishment of Warning Areas in the Airspace Overlying the Waters Between 3 and 12 Nautical Miles From the United States Coast

rindock.textblock: [Docket No. 25767; Special Federal Aviation Regulation (SFAR) No. 53-3]

summary.textblock: This document corrects an error to the Final Rule, on ``Establishment of Warning Areas in the Airspace Overlying the Waters Between 3 and 12 Nautical Miles From the United States Coast'', which was published on Wednesday, December 29, 1993 (58 FR 69128). The Amendment No. was omitted.
